Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: At 4th level, a heartwarder's kiss confers a state of bliss upon its recipient, conferring a +2 morale bonus on attacks, weapon damage, checks, and saves. This ability lasts 5 rounds, and can be used five times per day. The one downside to a heartwarder's kiss is that it also dazes the subject for one round.
Use: Selected.